# Rclone filter for C:\Dev -> OneDrive Dev
# Default behavior is include unless a rule below excludes it.

# Operational sync files
# Keep the sync scripts/config backed up, but do not mirror logs or transient auth/lock files.
- /.sync/logs/**
- /.sync/auth/**
- /.sync/*.lock
+ /.sync/**

# Root-level non-workspace/system folders that should not be mirrored from C:\Dev
- /AppData/**
- /Microsoft/**
- /Windows/**
- /nvim-data/**
- /.claude/**
- /.claude.json
- /.claude.json.*
- **/.claude/**

# Secrets, credentials, local machine state, and private runtime configuration
+ **/.env.example
+ **/.env.sample
+ **/.env.template
- **/.env
- **/.env.*
- **/.envrc
- **/*credential*
- **/*credentials*
- **/*secret*
- **/*secrets*
- **/*token*
- **/*auth*
- **/id_rsa
- **/id_ed25519
- **/*.pem
- **/*.key
- **/*.pfx

# VCS metadata
- **/.git/**
- **/.hg/**
- **/.svn/**

# Dependency/vendor directories
- **/node_modules/**
- **/.venv/**
- **/venv/**
- **/env/**
- **/.tox/**
- **/.vendor/**
- **/vendor/**

# Python/tool caches
- **/__pycache__/**
- **/.pytest_cache/**
- **/.ruff_cache/**
- **/.mypy_cache/**
- **/.uv-cache/**
- **/.coverage
- **/.coverage.*

# Build outputs, generated sites, and framework caches
- **/dist/**
- **/build/**
- **/target/**
- **/bin/**
- **/obj/**
- **/public/**
- **/resources/_gen/**
- **/pagefind/**
- **/graphify-out/**
- **/.hugo_build.lock
- **/.next/**
- **/.turbo/**
- **/.cache/**
- **/coverage/**
- **/out/**
- **/.tmp/**
- **/tmp/**
- **/rescue-usb-build/work/**
- **/.svelte-kit/**
- **/.nuxt/**
- **/.output/**
- **/.docusaurus/**
- **/.vite/**
- **/.parcel-cache/**
- **/.angular/**
- **/.astro/**
- **/.vercel/**
- **/.netlify/**
- **/.wrangler/**
- **/storybook-static/**
- **/.nyc_output/**
- **/__pypackages__/**
- **/site-packages/**

# Logs, temporary files, dumps, and local OS/editor noise
- **/*.log
- **/*.tmp
- **/*.temp
- **/*.bak
- **/*.swp
- **/*.swo
- **/*.dmp
- **/*.dump
- /*.7z
- /*.rar
- /*.zip
- /*.tar
- /*.tgz
- /*.gz
- **/*.7z
- **/*.rar
- **/*.zip
- **/*.tar
- **/*.tgz
- **/*.gz
- **/*.safetensors
- **/*.onnx
- **/*.gguf
- **/*.pt
- **/*.pth
- **/*.ckpt
- **/Thumbs.db
- **/desktop.ini
- **/.DS_Store
